# .claude/archive-run.config
# Which metric collectors to run at archival time.
# Each line is a collector name (filename without .sh extension).
# Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# Uncomment the collectors relevant to your project.
# The 'git' collector is universal and recommended for all projects.

git

# Language-specific collectors (uncomment what applies):
# python
# node
# go
# rust

# Code duplication (jscpd) is NOT a collector script — run it manually.
# See archive-run SKILL.md for the recommended command with --min-lines 5 --min-tokens 50.
